      *                          * Se si e' sulla prima pagina         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    not  > w-lin-num-lin-vis
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-cor
                     go to acc-cor-reg-998.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se non si e' sulla prima pagina     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-lin-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-985.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Slct da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-986.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rig-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il numero riga di destinazione   *
      *                          * risulta oltre il numero d'ordine    *
      *                          * attuale si sottrae 1 al numero ri-  *
      *                          * ga di destinazione                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-slc-num-rig    >    w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac
                     subtract  1          from w-cnt-slc-num-rig      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-987.
       acc-cor-reg-986.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-987.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Ad accettazione nr riga selezionato *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-slc-num-rig    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A inizio routine                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-990.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf1 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       acc-cor-reg-992.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf2 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Subroutine                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cor-reg-pf2-000  thru acc-cor-reg-pf2-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A inizio routine                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-994.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf3 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Subroutine                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cor-reg-pf3-000  thru acc-cor-reg-pf3-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A inizio routine                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-996.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf4 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Subroutine                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cor-reg-pf4-000  thru acc-cor-reg-pf4-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A inizio routine                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-998.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento status di impostazione corpo       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-max        =    zero
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-imp-cor
           else      move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Abblencamento note in righe documento           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   w-vis-not-rgd-top      .
           perform   vis-not-rgd-000      thru vis-not-rgd-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione corpo a partire dalla riga con numero d'or-  *
      *    * dine : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Trattamento tasto Pf2                                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cor-reg-pf2-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio video attuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione dati identificativi ordine cliente *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RO"                 to   l-dup-orf-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/bfo/prg/obj/pbfo300c"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-dup-orf
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito operazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        l-dup-orf-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-pf2-200.
       acc-cor-reg-pf2-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set del flag di trattamento ordine cliente      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-dup-orf-flg-orf      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione prompts    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata a zero  *
      *              * per forzare la rivisualizzazione                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-pf2-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino video precedentemente salvato        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Rimozione record dalla catena                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-pf2-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione corpo a partire dalla riga con numero d'or-  *
      *    * dine : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Trattamento tasto Pf3                                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cor-reg-pf3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio video attuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione dati identificativi bolla da du-   *
      *              * plicare                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RB"                 to   l-dup-rdb-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/bfo/prg/obj/pbfo300e"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-dup-rdb
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito operazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        l-dup-rdb-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-pf3-200.
       acc-cor-reg-pf3-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set del flag di trattamento bolla da duplicare  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-dup-rdb-flg-bfo      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione prompts    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata a zero  *
      *              * per forzare la rivisualizzazione                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-pf3-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino video precedentemente salvato        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Rimozione record dalla catena                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-pf3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione corpo a partire dalla riga con numero d'or-  *
      *    * dine : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Trattamento tasto Pf4                                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cor-reg-pf4-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio video attuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se bolla a fronte ordine fornitore         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmb-maf    =    02
                     go to acc-cor-reg-pf4-200
           else      go to acc-cor-reg-pf4-400.
       acc-cor-reg-pf4-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione dati identificativi ordine forni-  *
      *              * tore                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   l-eva-orf-tip-ope      .
           move      w-tes-cod-tmb-dmf    to   l-eva-orf-tmo-orf      .
           move      "pgm/bfo/prg/obj/pbfo300a"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-eva-orf
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito operazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        l-eva-orf-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-pf4-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Confronto testata ordine fornitore richiamato   *
      *              * con testata documento in corso di trattamento   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "T+"                 to   l-eva-orf-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/bfo/prg/obj/pbfo300a"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-eva-orf
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se esito operazione negativo : riciclo su   *
      *                  * accettazione dati identificativi ordine     *
      *                  * fornitore                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        l-eva-orf-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-pf4-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set del flag di trattamento ordine fornitore    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-eva-orf-flg-orf      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A set dei flag di visualizzazione e conti-  *
      *                  * nuazione                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-pf4-300.
       acc-cor-reg-pf4-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione prompts    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata a zero  *
      *              * per forzare la rivisualizzazione                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-pf4-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino video precedentemente salvato        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Rimozione record dalla catena                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-pf4-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrp-dav   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cor-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate, escluse fincature        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-cor-reg-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine del primo numero *
      *              * riga da visualizzare                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrp-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           subtract  w-lin-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine dell'ultimo nu-  *
      *              * mero riga da visualizzare                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           add       w-lin-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione numero pagina in corso di trat- *
      *              * tamento                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cor-reg-npg-000  thru vis-cor-reg-npg-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Operazione di Start su catena movimenti         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start errata : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-cor-reg-999.
       vis-cor-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale catena movimenti            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine lettura : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-cor-reg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work di  *
      *              * lavoro                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riga singolo movimento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero riga da visualizzare          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se oltre ultima riga da visualizzare       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    not  > w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                     go to vis-cor-reg-200.
       vis-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo                              *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Numero pagina corpo                                       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cor-reg-npg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero di pagina                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione pagina attuale               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cat-rig-max
                                        giving w-cnt-cor-pag-max
                                     remainder w-cnt-cor-pag-rem      .
           if        w-cnt-cor-pag-rem    >    zero
                     add 1                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-max      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                                        giving w-cnt-cor-pag-att      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing pagina attuale                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-att    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-ep1      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing pagina finale                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-max    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-ep2      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
           string    "["
                                delimited by   size
                     w-cnt-cor-pag-ep1
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "/"
                                delimited by   size
                     w-cnt-cor-pag-ep2
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "]"
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Allineamento al centro                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      09                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-npa    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           perform   all-str-cen-000      thru all-str-cen-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riempimento con '-'                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           inspect   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa
                                     replacing all " " by   "-"       .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      09                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      37                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-npa    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-cor-reg-npg-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-cor-reg-npg-999.
       vis-cor-reg-npg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione linea corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Abblencamento immagine linea di corpo           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-imm              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero linea assoluta a video    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                                        giving w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003
                                     remainder w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-prc    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       w-lin-pri-lin-vid    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo visualizzazione riga               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "I"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-100
           else if   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "S"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-200
           else if   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "N"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-300
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-400.
       vis-lin-cor-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione indicatore linea         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "==>"                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero linea a spaces    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero d'ordine riga     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione riga intera              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-405.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga in append : uscita              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rig-lst        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-lin-cor-999.
       vis-lin-cor-410.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing Numero d'ordine riga            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
       vis-lin-cor-415.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga di tipo New : fine editing      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-lin-cor-800.
       vis-lin-cor-450.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing segnale tipo riga reale         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-bld-rgb (1)    =    1
                     move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-seg-trr      .
       vis-lin-cor-500.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing descrizione                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-lin-cor-des-000  thru vis-lin-cor-des-999    .
       vis-lin-cor-550.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Quantita' e prezzo                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Editing quantita'                   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   w-edt-qta-inc-ope      .
      *
           if        w-rig-snx-tum (1)    =    "P"
                     move  w-rig-qta-acq (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-qta
           else if   w-rig-snx-tum (1)    =    "S"
                     move  w-rig-qta-acq (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-qta
           else      move  w-rig-qta-fda (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-qta      .
      *
           if        w-rig-snx-tum (1)    =    "P"
                     move  w-rig-dec-qta (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-dec
           else if   w-rig-snx-tum (1)    =    "S"
                     move  w-rig-nde-tum (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-dec
           else      move  w-rig-dec-qta (1)
                                          to   w-edt-qta-inc-dec      .
      *
           move      "S"                  to   w-edt-qta-inc-sgn      .
           move      11                   to   w-edt-qta-inc-car      .
           perform   edt-qta-inc-000      thru edt-qta-inc-999        .
           move      w-edt-qta-inc-edt    to   w-lin-imm-qta-fda      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Editing prezzo                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           if        w-rig-prz-acq (1)    >    9999999
                     move  09             to   v-car
           else      move  07             to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           add       w-rig-dec-prz (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           if        w-rig-prz-acq (1)    >    9999999
                     move  "B"            to   v-edm
           else      move  "GB"           to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-prz-acq (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-prz-acq      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Continuazione                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-650.
       vis-lin-cor-650.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing importo                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           if        w-rig-imp-rig (1)    >    9999999999 or
                     w-rig-imp-rig (1)    <   -9999999999
                     if    w-tes-dec-vpf (1)
                                          =    0
                           move  13       to   v-car
                     else  move  12       to   v-car
           else      move  10             to   v-car                  .
           subtract  w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    from v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           if        w-rig-imp-rig (1)    >    9999999999 or
                     w-rig-imp-rig (1)    <   -9999999999
                     move  "B"            to   v-edm
           else      move  "GB"           to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-imp-rig (1)    to   v-num                  .
           if        w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    =    1
                     divide 10            into v-num
           else if   w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    =    2
                     divide 100           into v-num
           else if   w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    =    3
                     divide 1000          into v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-imp-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Eventuale segnale di difformita' del-   *
      *                      * l'importo per effetto dell'accettazione *
      *                      * manuale                                 *
      *                      *                                         *
      *                      * N.B.: DA IMPLEMENTARE                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Parametri per visualizzazione           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
       vis-lin-cor-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione visualizzazione prima linea          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-lin-imm-dsp-lin (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se una sola linea : uscita                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-num-lin-prc    =    1
                     go to vis-lin-cor-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione visualizzazione altre linee          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003      .
       vis-lin-cor-925.
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003      .
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003    >    w-lin-num-lin-prc
                     go to vis-lin-cor-999.
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-lin-imm-dsp-lin
                    (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003)   to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-925.
       vis-lin-cor-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione linea corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Numero pagina corpo                                       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-des-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda del tipo riga              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "P"  and
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tfu (1)
                                          =    spaces ) or
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "M"      or
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "V"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-100
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-des-800.
       vis-lin-cor-des-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se il tipo riga indica che si sta trattando un  *
      *              * codice di magazzino                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda della personalizzazio- *
      *                  * ne di tipo esposizione descrizione          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    00
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-200
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    01
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-210
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    02
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-220
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    03
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-230
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    04
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-240
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    05
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-250
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    06
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-260
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    11
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-310
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    12
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-320
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    13
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-330
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    14
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-340
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    21
                     go to vis-lin-cor-des-410
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-des-200.
       vis-lin-cor-des-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 00                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A visualizzazione dell'intera descrizione   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-800.
       vis-lin-cor-des-210.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 01                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing primi 25 caratteri della descrizio- *
      *                  * ne                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d25-p01      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p01      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-220.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 02                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing primi 21 caratteri della descrizio- *
      *                  * ne                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d21-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi sinistra                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing tipo codice di magazzino            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    04
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi destra                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-230.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 03                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p03      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing primi 25 caratteri della descrizio- *
      *                  * ne                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d25-p03      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-240.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 04                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi sinistra                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p04      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing tipo codice di magazzino            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    04
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi destra                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p04      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p04      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing primi 21 caratteri della descrizio- *
      *                  * ne                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d21-p04      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-250.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 05                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p01      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-260.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 06                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi sinistra                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing tipo codice di magazzino            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    04
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi destra                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p02      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-310.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 11                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing segnale codice fornitore            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[F]"                to   w-lin-imm-pfp-p11      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice secondo il fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cop-sfn (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cdf-p11      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p11      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-320.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 12                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing segnale codice fornitore            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[F]"                to   w-lin-imm-pfp-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice secondo il fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cop-sfn (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cdf-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi sinistra                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing tipo codice di magazzino            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p12
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p12
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p12
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    04
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p12
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi destra                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p12      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-330.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 13                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing segnale codice fornitore            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[F]"                to   w-lin-imm-pfp-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice secondo il fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cop-sfn (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cdf-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-340.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 14                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi sinistra                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing tipo codice di magazzino            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p14
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p14
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p14
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    04
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p14
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing parentesi destra                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing segnale codice fornitore            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[F]"                to   w-lin-imm-pfp-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice secondo il fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cop-sfn (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cdf-p14      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-410.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 21                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice magazzino                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-mag (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing segnale codice casa produttrice     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[P]"                to   w-lin-imm-pfp-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura archivio [aaq]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-tip-mag (1)    to   w-let-arc-aaq-tpm      .
           move      w-rig-num-mag (1)    to   w-let-arc-aaq-cdm      .
           perform   let-arc-aaq-000      thru let-arc-aaq-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice secondo il fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-aaq-cdp    to   w-lin-imm-cdf-p13      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se il tipo riga indica che non si sta trattando *
      *              * un codice di magazzino: a visualizzazione della *
      *              * sola intera descrizione                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-des-rig      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-des-900.
       vis-lin-cor-des-900.
