           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-------------- -------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
